ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: We don't really have a choice not to take history.

I would recommend this class with Professor Guinnane as an enjoyable, stimulating, and painless way to complete the economic history requirement. Even if there was no such requirement, I would recommend this course as a way to see the content of our first year courses in action.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: To be honest, I do not think this course is helpful for all of the economics students. Perhaps it is useful for a small amount of the class, but not in general.
